isToMany

public boolean isToMany()
Tells whether relationship from source to target is to-one or to-many. If one-to-many, getxxx() method of the data object class would return a list, otherwise it returns a single DataObject There is explicitly no setToMany on Relationship.. only DbRelationship supports such a notion, and ObjRelationship derives it's value from the underlying DbRelationship(s)
